cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the accurate detection of fingertips in depth images using a convolutional neural network. It may also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as fingertip detection is important for human-robot interaction. Additionally, it could be categorized under Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) as it involves the interaction between humans and computers. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible sub-categories as the paper uses a neural network and deals with image data.
